original_title: Vamp: I full symfoni II - Med Kringkastingsorkesteret
overview: Vamp and the Norwegian Radio Orchestra teams up with Eivór Pálsdóttir of the Faroe Islands to recreate and unite the magic of the 2 culture institutions created 5 years ago. 2 sold out shows created the perfect atmosphere for a live concert.
title: Vamp In Symphony With The Norwegian Radio Orchestra II
